U.S. Iron and Steel Scrap Use and Stockpiles for June

-- B y   S t e p h e n   R o s e
-- 
2011-09-29T20:15:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/u-s-iron-and-steel-scrap-use-and-stockpiles-for-june-table-.html
Following is a table detailing U.S.
iron and steel-scrap and pig-iron receipts, production,  
consumption, shipments and stockpiles for June, according to
the U.S Geological Survey in Reston,  Virginia . Iron and steel
scrap are used in the production of new steel and cast-iron
products. Automobiles are the primary source of steel scrap.  
